# Cursor Project Rules

> See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for complete project context.

## Quick Rules

- **Mobile-first**: Base styles = mobile, add `md:`, `lg:` for larger
- **Untyped Supabase**: No `<Database>` generics
- **Use adminClient**: For all DB operations in API routes
- **Dark theme**: `bg-slate-950`, `text-slate-100`, `border-slate-800`
- **Tailwind only**: No inline styles or CSS modules
